      <p>Wago.io seeks to create a sustainable ecosystem that helps benefit both users and developers. As such, Wago.io supports the display of advertisements in connection with Wago.io applications and pages. Doing so helps the developers who contribute to Wago.io get fairly compensated for the time and effort they put into their work. In addition, this helps provide a stream of new applications, tools, and functionality that users can benefit from. We enforce strict guidelines with our advertising partners to ensure that it leads to the best possible user experience. If you have any feedback on the user advertisement experience please do not hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:info@wago.io">info@wago.io</a>protected.</p><p>The Wago.io platform also supports opting out of in-app ads, by providing app developers the option to integrate a paid subscription plan for their app. It is up to the developer of the app to decide whether to include a subscription plan for the app or not.</p><p>Advertising service providers may personalize the ads they deliver to make them more relevant to you. This is based upon information they collect independently, and is stored in cookies. In addition, to support personalization of in-app ads, Wago.io may provide limited information to advertising service providers when they deliver advertisements which users are welcome to opt out of through their account settings.</p>
