    <collapsible title="Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act">
      <p>Minors and children should not use Wago.io. By using the Wago.io, you represent that you have the legal capacity to enter into a binding agreement.</p><p>Wago.io does not knowingly collect or store any Personal Information from children under thirteen (13) in the United States or under the relevant age threshold in other jurisdictions where the child is located. If you are under thirteen (13) years old in the United States, or under the relevant age threshold in the jurisdiction where you are located, you cannot use Wago.io without the permission of your parent or guardian.</p><p>However, we may collect technical information required for delivering the service and for the support of our internal operations from all users of our Wago.io. If parents or guardians believe that we have unintentionally collected their children’s other Personal Information or otherwise used their children’s Personal Information for another purpose, they may reach out to us at <a href="mailto:info@wago.io">info@wago.io</a>. Parents should contact us immediately if they have any concerns.</p>
